===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ar}} {{term|القرآن|القُرْآن|tr=al-qur’ān|lang=ar}}, definite form of {{term|قرآن||recitation|tr=qur'ān|lang=ar}}, from {{term|قراءة||reading, recitation|lang=ar|tr=qirā’a}}, from {{term|قرأ||to declaim, to recite|lang=ar|tr=qará’a}}, apparently after {{etyl|syc}} {{term|ܩܪܝܢܐ||reading; scripture|lang=syc|sc=Syrc|tr=qeriānā}}.

